<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3765354>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Drawing of transverse sections of leaves of three graminoid species of Dendrobium. A. Total section of D. unicarinatum Kores (H.S. MacKee 44925).Vascular bundles arerepresented by empty circles and are numbered starting from the lamina margin, black spots indicate fibre bundles. B. Leaf margins sections, a. D. letocartiorum Munzinger & M.Pignal sp. nov. (H.S. MacKee 37760); b. D. camaridiorum Rchb.f. (H.S. MacKee 24639). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3765354/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

